title: [Hunting Lodge, Findings]
description: Beneath an exposed oak rafter ceiling, a mounted puma head hangs on one of the stone wainscoted walls.  A heavy stained glass display case and a wide knotted oak counter sit in opposite corners while a mounted and stuffed massive pyrothag rests on a worn grey flagstone floor.
